{"tid":1439863,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人想知香港個WESG 電競比賽有幾垃圾?","createTime":"2019-08-10T08:57:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T14:09:23.000Z","uid":18333,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9bfa62b5cc51f62d45bfdee2196c7b6e537403d4","tid":1439863,"uid":18333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T08:57:09.000Z","msg":"有冇人想知香港個WESG 電競比賽有幾垃圾?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fJ51m8n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfJ51m8n.jpg&h=b78c0d81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我唔知係外判定係點<br />\n開會講普通話<br />\n旁述要坐food court D台凳做解說<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DEuafra.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDEuafra.jpg&h=9e576ed7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nD工作人員係道睇戲, 睇END GAME, 等收工<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vAGoArk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvAGoArk.jpg&h=827303a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n成個場極度少人<br />\nCAM 同打燈又係超級有問題<br />\n揀埋D 星期一~五時間黎打比賽, 痴痴地線<br />\n假借電競名義牟利斂財<br />\n賽評和選手慘淪為佢地既發財工具<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我仲想講, 我大陸既朋友<br />\n佢地大陸搞既WESG 同樣係中飽私囊, 貪到仆街, 預算拎去分晒比自己友<br />\n成個比賽除左獎金之外, 全部都得個樣<br />\n真係打撚完都唔知有搞過比賽咁<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我真係估唔到香港都有一日會出現呢D 咁既情況"},{"pid":"2ffd97a12ea14a97ff960e678e7f52dd4fed7404","tid":1439863,"uid":18333,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T09:00:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f5P16Bg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff5P16Bg.jpg&h=a1cf90f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我就真係好想問佢地D Sponsor<br />\n你地贊助緊既比賽, 究竟班人搞緊乜鳩"},{"pid":"5311456dcfddcb1494e2951df575b4fdad4bf454","tid":1439863,"uid":189140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T12:57:48.000Z","msg":"冰山一角<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢行太多仆街野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"857a4137b2d7a45db03641b1674b1db745cb68c1","tid":1439863,"uid":184570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:10:18.000Z","msg":"慘. 香港電競就係比班仆街商人賺錢"},{"pid":"01250e9a1260260323bff9795e4b4032e9c03d0f","tid":1439863,"uid":140454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T10:25:19.000Z","msg":"預撚左啦<br />\n連個最基本既聯賽都無<br />\n你覺得真係有心搞咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d645e602f83acffb434ea4741bdd090518cfa611","tid":1439863,"uid":11319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T13:35:20.000Z","msg":"有冇比賽真係打緊?"},{"pid":"41eea7f57d494ef97b7f33c07554b213bbe11008","tid":1439863,"uid":51349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d645e602f83acffb434ea4741bdd090518cfa611","tid":1439863,"uid":11319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T13:35:20.000Z","msg":"有冇比賽真係打緊?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T13:43:41.000Z","msg":"有<br />\n利申:選手,星期1-5打真係世界級"},{"pid":"f5c31b36c811c3964344e8a34e7e19ee5518fa8f","tid":1439863,"uid":215249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T14:09:23.000Z","msg":"香港不嬲都係咁<br />\n唔係第一日既事"}]}